      "body" : "Do you really think, <code>2 * (long) Integer.MAX_VALUE + 2</code> is easier to understand than <code>0x1_0000_0000L</code>? In that regard, why not simply <code>return signed &amp; 0xFFFF_FFFFL;</code>?"
