    "answer_id" : 34744113,
    "question_id" : 9854166,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Perhaps this is what you meant?</p>\n\n<pre><code>long getUnsigned(int signed) {\n    return signed &gt;= 0 ? signed : 2 * (long) Integer.MAX_VALUE + 2 + signed;\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li><code>getUnsigned(0)</code> → 0</li>\n<li><code>getUnsigned(1)</code> → 1</li>\n<li><code>getUnsigned(Integer.MAX_VALUE)</code> → 2147483647</li>\n<li><code>getUnsigned(Integer.MIN_VALUE)</code> → 2147483648</li>\n<li><code>getUnsigned(Integer.MIN_VALUE + 1)</code> → 2147483649</li>\n</ul>\n"
