    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Just made this piece of code, wich converts \"this.altura\" from negative to positive number. Hope this helps someone in need</p>\n\n<pre><code>       if(this.altura &lt; 0){    \n\n                        String aux = Integer.toString(this.altura);\n                        char aux2[] = aux.toCharArray();\n                        aux = \"\";\n                        for(int con = 1; con &lt; aux2.length; con++){\n                            aux += aux2[con];\n                        }\n                        this.altura = Integer.parseInt(aux);\n                        System.out.println(\"New Value: \" + this.altura);\n                    }\n</code></pre>\n"
